Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mám narodeninovú oslavu.\NChcem aby si prišla.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Posledné dni sa s tebou dobre rozpráva, Fujinuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To pretože som sa rozhodol, že ti nebudem klamať.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Povedal som to nahlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-Hinazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uvidíme sa zajtra!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toto je posledné miesto, kde som videl pred 18-timi rokmi Hinazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jej telo sa našlo až potom, čo sa roztopil sneh,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}ale v ktorý deň v marci zmizla?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:36.06,Crash,NTP,0,0,0,,Dievča
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:36.31,Crash,NTP,0,0,0,,Izolácia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:36.56,Crash,NTP,0,0,0,,Zmiznutie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:36.82,Crash,NTP,0,0,0,,Únos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.27,Crash,NTP,0,0,0,,SMRŤ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keby som si len tak vedel spomenúť kedy sa to stalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:51.33,Sign Left,NTP,0,0,0,,AYA NAKANISHI\N(11 ROKOV)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:51.33,Sign Right,NTP,0,0,0,,KAYO HINAZUKI\N(10 ROKOV)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:51.33,SignNC,NTP,0,0,0,,HIROMI SUGITA\N(11 ROKOV)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aya Nakanishi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hiromi Sugita...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hiromi Souda, tiež...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:53.96,SignNC,NTP,0,0,0,,KAYO HINAZUKI\N(10 ROKOV)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale vtedy mala Hinazuki len 10 rokov.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.50,0:00:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inými slovami, keď Hinazuki zmizla v marci,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}ešte nemala narodeniny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:01:06.97,Sign,NTP,0,0,0,,MAREC
